'''瑞玛·班达尔·沙特'''公主（全名'''Reema bint Bandar bin Sultan bin Abdulaziz Al Saud'''，{{lang-ar|ريما بنت بندر بن سلطان آل سعود}}）是[[沙烏地阿拉伯|沙烏地阿拉伯]]公主、同時也是一位企業家與慈善家。

生於[[沙特|沙特]]的[[利雅德|利雅德]]，為[[班达尔·本·苏尔坦·阿勒沙特|班达尔·本·苏尔坦亲王]]和 {{le|Haifa bint Faisal|Haifa bint Faisal}} 的女兒。Bandar bin Sultan 王子在1983年至2005年曾擔任沙特駐美國大使，因此瑞玛·班达尔·沙特公主在美國[[華盛頓特區|華盛頓特區]]长大<ref name="nytimes1">{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/03/world/middleeast/saudi-women-make-small-but-significant-strides-in-the-work-force.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 | title=In Taking Jobs, Women Take on a Saudi Taboo | publisher=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]] | date=2013-12-02 | accessdate=2016-10-21 | archive-date=2019-02-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190224115743/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/03/world/middleeast/saudi-women-make-small-but-significant-strides-in-the-work-force.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[https://www.saudiembassy.net/news/princess-reema-bint-bandar-arrives-washington-dc-begin-assignment-saudi-ambassador-us “Princess Reema bint Bandar Arrives in Washington, DC to Begin Assignment as Saudi Ambassador to the U.S.”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.saudiembassy.net/news/princess-reema-bint-bandar-arrives-washington-dc-begin-assignment-saudi-ambassador-us |date=20201203221146 }} Saudi Embassy, Washington D.C., [03-07-2019]</ref>，並於[[喬治華盛頓大學|喬治華盛頓大學]]取得博物館研究學士學位<ref name="fastcompany1">{{cite web | url=http://www.fastcompany.com/3029166/most-creative-people-2014/princess-reema-bint-bandar-al-saud | title=Most Creative People 2014 | publisher=Fast Company | date=2014-05-12 | accessdate=2016-10-21 | archive-date=2014-12-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221043654/http://www.fastcompany.com/3029166/most-creative-people-2014/princess-reema-bint-bandar-al-saud | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2005年，Reema 公主返回沙特，有感女性參與公共事務受到限制，因此在2008年成立組織 Alf Khair，為女性提供培訓和資源，讓她們加入社會勞動行列<ref name="autogenerated1">{{cite web | url=http://www.thnk.org/people-of-thnk/person/reema-bint-bandar-al-saud/ | title=Reema Bint Bandar Al Saud | publisher=THNK School of Creative Leadership | accessdate=2016-10-21 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815000648/http://www.thnk.org/people-of-thnk/person/reema-bint-bandar-al-saud/ | archivedate=2016-08-15 }}</ref><ref>[http://english.alarabiya.net/en/features/2019/02/24/Princess-Reema-bint-Bandar-Saudi-Arabia-s-first-female-ambassador.html# “Princess Reema bint Bandar: Saudi Arabia’s first female ambassador”] {{Wayback|url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/features/2019/02/24/Princess-Reema-bint-Bandar-Saudi-Arabia-s-first-female-ambassador.html |date=20201107223307 }} Al Arabiya [24-02-2019]</ref>。瑞玛公主曾指，將女性納入勞動力，是一項「進化，而非西方化」（evolution, not Westernization）<ref name="nytimes1"/> 。2016年8月1日，Reema 公主被任命為國家體育總局轄下女性體育部門的首長，外界期望這會是沙特放寬女性參與運動的預兆。

2019年2月，她被任命为沙特的第十一任驻美国大使，她的弟弟Khalid則成為沙特驻英国大使。<ref>[https://www.thenational.ae/world/mena/saudi-princess-reema-bint-bandar-sworn-in-as-kingdom-s-ambassador-to-washington-1.849761 “Saudi Princess Reema bint Bandar sworn in as Kingdom's ambassador to Washington”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.thenational.ae/world/mena/saudi-princess-reema-bint-bandar-sworn-in-as-kingdom-s-ambassador-to-washington-1.849761 |date=20190505092630 }} The National [16-04-2019]</ref>

